{"tid":2390094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"售貨員認用膠欄堵路准保釋候判 辯稱當日原是往購物","createTime":"2021-02-01T10:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T10:56:36.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f2fd7bec4e59667137f399fd2b899522addd25d8","tid":2390094,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:30:30.000Z","msg":"市民去年5月在銅鑼灣發起流水式遊行，反對訂立國安法，遭警方施放催淚彈驅散，其間有年輕售貨員涉用膠欄堵路。他今承認在公眾地方造成阻礙罪。辯方求情指，被告原本打算前往購物，一時衝動下才將膠圍欄掟出路面，事前沒有預謀。主任裁判官<span class=\"red\">錢禮</span>下令索取社會服務令報告及感化報告，押後案件至3月1日判刑，<span class=\"red\">被告獲准保釋候判</span>。"},{"pid":"97058e4680c9f6f841001da391309e4fe514f86e","tid":2390094,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:30:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/I7SDH2KPUJGAPAPTPBDVWXJBNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2FI7SDH2KPUJGAPAPTPBDVWXJBNI%2F&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=135e3aac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2FI7SDH2KPUJGAPAPTPBDVWXJBNI%2F&h=8f8b8be6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/I7SDH2KPUJGAPAPTPBDVWXJBNI/</a>"},{"pid":"d8a25aea651869986acacfe272044bc523f4b6b3","tid":2390094,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145370f34d66859cc45d10d287e0c12300fd146a","tid":2390094,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:48:16.000Z","msg":"其實正常都俾保釋呀嘛"},{"pid":"926204158022a2f3b6d3e2b195e7808e7ede935e","tid":2390094,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"建議著草"}]}